Select Template

 

While creating an object you are able to select the template which to be used for presenting it. By default is selected the primary template. The list with templates is filtered based on the data entered in the New screen.

Once you create the item, you will be only able to change its template by using Change template action.

To select a template use the Template drop down menu which gives you all available options including Blank one.
